divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving down the road, I snapped a picture of a crashed Citylink bus to show my husband. I was going to show my husband the picture of the crash when he got home from work and noticed the object. I had no idea what it was. I was just curious if it was a UFO or not. I noticed it in the picture when I checked it.
